WEBVTT

00:03.449 --> 00:04.570
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.571 --> 00:06.071
<i>Jessica found Chester</i>
<i>in a hotel room</i>

00:06.072 --> 00:07.072
<i>with another woman,</i>

00:07.073 --> 00:09.074
<i>and told him he had better find</i>

00:09.075 --> 00:10.576
<i>another place to live.</i>

00:10.577 --> 00:12.077
<i>Jodie found out</i>
<i>someone had complained</i>

00:12.078 --> 00:14.079
<i>to the welfare department</i>
<i>about him.</i>

00:14.080 --> 00:15.581
<i>Dutch found out</i>

00:15.582 --> 00:17.583
<i>Eunice has been fooling around</i>
<i>with another man,</i>

00:17.584 --> 00:21.587
<i>and Jessica met Billy's teacher</i>
<i>and found her very nice.</i>

00:21.588 --> 00:23.088
<i>Want to find out more?</i>

00:23.089 --> 00:26.092
<i>Stay tuned</i>
<i>for this episode of...</i> Soap.

