<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:33.099 --> 00:35.100
<i>Jessica Tate</i>

00:35.101 --> 00:37.603
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:37.604 --> 00:41.106
<i>These are the Tates,</i>

00:41.107 --> 00:45.110
<i>and these are the Campbells,</i>

